title: The Cootees - Let's Play House
description:
The Cootees were an American punk rock band. MxPx members Mike Herrera and Tom Wisniewski joined with Dale Yob (Ninety Pound Wuss and Slick Shoes[1]) and a mutual friend, Jiles O'Neal.
